high_descs: Take black plate from the sink.
Turn right, turn right, walk to refrigerator.
Put plate in refrigerator, close door, wait a short time, take plate from refrigerator.
Got to cabinet immediately to left of refrigerator.
Open cabinet door and put plate on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate on bottom shelf in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the sink.
Take the plate out of the sink.
Go to the right to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the plate in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the plate out and shut the door again.
Move to the left and face the lower cabinet to the left of the fridge.
Put the plate in the cabinet left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate in the cabinet.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the black plate that is in the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the black plate inside on the top shelf, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the plate, then close the door again.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter to the left of the fridge.
Open the rightmost cabinet door below the counter and put the chilled plate inside the cabinet then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate in a cabinet.
